<node id="Residual Network">
  <data key="d0">Residual Network</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">A proposed neural network architecture that can serve as the backbone for computer vision tasks and brings 28% relative performance improvement when adopted.&lt;SEP&gt;A deep neural network architecture whose core performance properties are documented in the ResNet academic paper.&lt;SEP&gt;A core deep neural network architecture that is easier to optimize, supports extremely high depth, solves the vanishing gradient problem, and delivers state-of-the-art performance across multiple computer vision tasks.</data>
  <data key="d3">doc-db198435de3fb87f4348eaba3adebc08-chunk-001&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6482cf54d681bbb3ef97680f6ba8ccf9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-224a1bf37b4ddb69909cb94d50546310</data>
