<node id="ResNet">
  <data key="d0">ResNet</data>
  <data key="d1">artifact</data>
  <data key="d2">The residual neural network architecture designed to simplify the training process of extremely deep neural networks, using residual connections.&lt;SEP&gt;A widely used classic deep convolutional neural network architecture proposed in 2015, with numerous variants adopted in half of ongoing deep learning applications.&lt;SEP&gt;A deep residual neural network model that achieved top rankings across multiple 2015 computer vision competitions.&lt;SEP&gt;A deep learning residual network architecture that solves the network depth degradation problem to deliver accuracy gains when increasing network depth.</data>
