<node id="ResNet lecture slide with training plots, performance table and presenter (10:17 frame) (image)">
  <data key="d0">ResNet lecture slide with training plots, performance table and presenter (10:17 frame) (image)</data>
  <data key="d1">image</data>
  <data key="d2">This lecture frame matches the 10:17 narration: it displays intuitive comparative training error plots (Figure 4) plus a precise numerical performance table (Table 2) to demonstrate that residual networks solve the deep plain network performance degradation problem on ImageNet, with an overlaid presenter delivering the explanation.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-5b31be4e965ce3cdd34dbb96723178c4</data>
