  <data key="d0">Deep Residual Learning Framework</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">A deep learning framework that solves the problem of deep neural network performance degradation by making stacked non-linear layers fit residual mapping directly.&lt;SEP&gt;A proposed deep learning method that uses identity shortcut connections to solve the problem of training and accuracy degradation in very deep neural networks</data>
