  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Rectified Linear Unit, an activation function used at multiple stages in the residual learning building block processing flow.&lt;SEP&gt;A common neural network activation function applied to the stacked weight layers inside the ResNet residual unit as shown in the ResNet paper</data>
