<node id="Bilibili">
  <data key="d0">Bilibili</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">Bilibili is a prominent, major public Chinese video sharing and hosting platform. It hosts a variety of educational content, including the specific deep learning, technical, and academic educational lectures that all of the analyzed video frames, lecture screenshots, referenced ResNet figures, and target content samples cited in the source descriptions are extracted from.

Across all of this hosted content, Bilibili applies its official platform branding via a distinct, faint, semi-transparent translucent watermark that features its official logo. This watermark is consistently positioned in the top right (upper right, far top right) corner of relevant video frames, lecture screenshots, ResNet figures, and target image frames, making the platform’s ownership of the content immediately identifiable on any sampled portion of the hosted lecture material.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-08bb6e363c70d359e2ce7a6941bbd296&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6482cf54d681bbb3ef97680f6ba8ccf9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-dd66735b57b907c822ab1b7be3272894&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f41f427d7692f82207c32ed93946e5d9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-eae59ad078e0dbf4b6e24318cf29eb84&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4fd7f66859f3f10e574d7b4fb7463262&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-61ba3e472890af88f7c2a6febec16473&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c5e8ad940693b6b92513e507d5fc585f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-df74ae1c57ae2c7bfba59933405fab52&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-fc7458f33135e8badd3be29282ef8dab&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d99389083ddf2c585966f6f00d11a412&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e9ce6d8d1214e88636b2d1368a3bb04b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-eaed664ca6fec6b1643d92a068cbfd8f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5d37ecff217107cadcd492318d68eaa4&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-60c47d631f7b153692d38285ddebb637&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a1f327f7896862c65aa57e4af22ac77f</data>
